            array('id' => '83','page_id' => '2','hints' => 'About-About','title' => 'W H Doctors Study Lab Ltd.','subtitle' => 'We help you to study in Abroad.','image' => 'upload/pageContent-image/20231109055414.png','description' => '<p>Study Abroad also has a well-organised platform in Bangladesh for student training for the preparation of IELTS and other relevant English language tests. We have liaison branches all over Bangladesh. No other educational training institute in Bangladesh has either such a vast network or student access as we do. This exclusive student base we currently have possesses great potential for overseas student recruitment. Our various services are comprehensive and tailored to suit students&rsquo; needs and budgets. All of our services aim to provide a student with personalised advice and information to help avoid unnecessary expenses until we are confident that a visa application by a student recruited by us has the best possible chance of success.</p>','number' => NULL,'button_text' => NULL,'button_link' => NULL,'is_not_deleteable' => '1','active_status' => '1','created_at' => '2023-11-09 05:54:14','updated_at' => '2024-03-04 23:33:35'),
            array('id' => '84','page_id' => '2','hints' => 'About-Mission','title' => 'Our Mission Statement','subtitle' => NULL,'image' => NULL,'description' => '<p>Most educators agree that immersion experiences are among the most lasting and meaningful types of education. Since our founding in 1970, we stand by our mission: &ldquo;International Field Studies is a non-profit organisation providing environmental education, scientific research, and cultural awareness through experiential learning.</p>','number' => NULL,'button_text' => NULL,'button_link' => NULL,'is_not_deleteable' => '1','active_status' => '1','created_at' => '2023-11-09 05:56:14','updated_at' => '2024-03-04 23:31:12'),
            array('id' => '85','page_id' => '2','hints' => 'About-What-we-do','title' => 'Our Services','subtitle' => NULL,'image' => NULL,'description' => '<p>International Field Studies, Inc. (IFS) is an educational and scientific non-profit organisation established to promote and assist educators with field study programmes. Established in 1970, IFS grew out of the increasing teacher interest in implementing field study experiences for their students with minimal organisational difficulty and expense. International Field Studies offers secondary schools, university groups, scientists, and other special-interest organisations field studies in four programme areas..... IFS continues to promote the concept of field studies as an important educational method. These experiential, outside-of-the classroom learning experiences are successful in almost every discipline, including the natural sciences, creative arts, history, and physical education. IFS believes an interdisciplinary approach to learning is especially well suited to the field studies environment. IFS functions as a facilitator for educational groups seeking expertise and logistical support. Staff members, experienced field instructors, and resource materials are available to assist educators and group leaders with educational development, site planning, and budgeting for a successful comprehensive field programme. By working with IFS to develop a proposed field study, teachers are able to offer their students high quality field study opportunities.</p>','number' => NULL,'button_text' => NULL,'button_link' => NULL,'is_not_deleteable' => '1','active_status' => '1','created_at' => '2023-11-09 05:56:55','updated_at' => '2024-03-04 23:34:50'),
            array('id' => '86','page_id' => '2','hints' => 'Sidebar-university-heading','title' => 'Find Your Next Destination...','subtitle' => NULL,'image' => NULL,'description' => NULL,'number' => NULL,'button_text' => NULL,'button_link' => NULL,'is_not_deleteable' => '1','active_status' => '1','created_at' => '2023-11-09 06:04:39','updated_at' => '2024-01-07 09:12:22'),
            array('id' => '92','page_id' => '2','hints' => 'Manage-app-heading','title' => 'Manage your projects from your mobile','subtitle' => 'Download the app to manage your projects, keep track of the progress and complete tasks without procastinating. Stay on track and complete on time!','image' => NULL,'description' => NULL,'number' => NULL,'button_text' => NULL,'button_link' => NULL,'is_not_deleteable' => '1','active_status' => '1','created_at' => '2023-11-09 06:25:50','updated_at' => '2024-01-07 07:59:13'),
